//⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⡆⠀⠀⠀⠀⢐⣢⣤⣵⡄⢀⠀⢀⢈⣉⠉⠉⠒⠤⠀⠿⠀⠀⠀⠀             Hold down left arrow = erase
//⠀⠀⠀⠀⠘⡇⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠉⠉⠁⠁⠈⠀⠸⢖⣿⣿⣷⠀⠀⢰⡆⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀           Right arrow = Draw⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
//⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⡇⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢀⠃⠀⡄⠀⠈⠉⠀⠀⠀⢴⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
